---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="NY SHIELD Act readiness for technology companies. Protect New York residents' data and meet breach notification requirements.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="NY SHIELD Act Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Protect New York residents' data. Implement reasonable safeguards. Meet breach notification requirements."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why the SHIELD Act Matters</h2>
    <p>The NY SHIELD Act applies to any business that holds private information of New York residents, regardless of where the business is located. Without reasonable safeguards, your organization faces AG enforcement, breach notification obligations, and market access risk.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Access the New York Market</h3>
        <p>The SHIELD Act applies to any business holding NY residents' private information, regardless of where the business is located. Operating in the New York market requires compliance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Meet Reasonable Safeguards Standard</h3>
        <p>The Act requires "reasonable" administrative, technical, and physical safeguards appropriate to the size and complexity of your business and the nature of the data you hold.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Prepare for Breach Notification</h3>
        <p>Expanded breach definitions and notification requirements affect incident response. The SHIELD Act broadened what counts as a breach and who must be notified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Demonstrate Due Diligence</h3>
        <p>Reasonable safeguards compliance demonstrates due diligence in the event of a breach investigation by the New York Attorney General.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your SHIELD Act compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Safeguard Implementation</h3>
        <p>Close gaps across admin, technical, and physical safeguards</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Breach Readiness</h3>
        <p>Notification procedures and incident response planning</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Ongoing Compliance</h3>
        <p>Annual reviews, training, and safeguard maintenance</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're implementing SHIELD Act safeguards for the first time or strengthening an existing program, we can help you build a readiness plan that fits your organization and data practices.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
